  <brief_title>Randomized Fixed Bearing vs Mobile Bearing Cruciate Retaining TKA</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multi-center, Prospective, Clinical Evaluation of the PFC Sigma Rotating Platform Cruciate Retaining Versus PFC Sigma Cruciate Retaining Knee Primary Cases</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
